Package org.agreement_technologies.common.map_planner

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CausalLink
    Common interface for causal links (a causal link represents a step supporting a precondition of another step).
    Condition
    Common interface for conditions (variable-value pairs that define preconditions and effects).
    ExtendedPlanner
    Extended planner interface.
    IPlan
    IPlan interface provides methods to work with incremental plans.
    OpenCondition
    Common interface for open conditions.
    Ordering
    Common interface for partial-order relationships among steps.
    Plan
    Basic interface of partial-order plans: extended by IPlan and HPlan and implemented by service.map_Planner.POPIncrementalPlan.
    Planner
    Common interface for planners.
    POPComparator
    Comparator interface for IPlans; extends the Comparator interface.
    POPSearchMethod
    Interface for the search method; manages the storage and extraction of partial order plans.
    Step
    Common interface for plan steps (actions inserted in a plan).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PlannerFactory
    Common base class for the planner factory: manages and creates planners
